					<![CDATA[
						 <p>Lovely writing, as usual from Tufto.<br /> No generic nitpicks but a personal one instead.<br /> Im suprised The Foundation refers to the area as Yellowstone and not as SCP-1422.<br /> I mean I get it, canons and all that, but still.<br /> Never the less, good introduction of characters, plot device and perfect execution.<br /> Another great Tufto piece.<br /> +1</p> <p>EDIT:<br /> Ah, I must have missread SCP-1422.<br /> Please disregard my personal nitpick.</p> 
				 	]]>
