						 <blockquote> <p>They were looking for <span style="text-decoration: underline;">&quot;the &quot;</span>, meaning of course a moment of eternity.</p> </blockquote> <p>A small question; is this an intentional expression?</p> <p>Also, Hammond's name is inconsistent; he is introduced as &quot;<em>Shaun</em> Hammond&quot;, and then mentioned as &quot;<em>John</em> Hammond&quot;.</p> <p>Aside from that, I thoroughly enjoyed this tragidy and I love this. +1.</p> 
				 	]]>
